It seems there's an issue executing the function call. However, based on your request to "Turn off cellular," I'll assume you want to disable cellular service.

The proper function call to disable cellular service would be:
```json
[
  {
    "name": "set_cellular_service_status",
    "arguments": {
      "on": false
    }
  }
]
```

This function call would disable cellular service by setting the 'on' parameter to false. Let me know if you'd like me to explain this further or if you have any other questions about cellular service settings.
